# Stripe Rules (Live Mode)

## Webhook Handler
- Single consolidated handler: `apps/api/src/routes/stripe/webhook.ts`
- ALWAYS use `stripe.webhooks.constructEvent()` with raw body (never pre-parsed JSON)
- Idempotency keys required on ALL `payment_intent` creates
- Verify signature on EVERY incoming webhook — no exceptions in dev/staging

## GAP-01 Status
Stripe webhook is dead — consolidate all handlers before deploy.

